        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Moderate and severe IUA according to the AFS IU adhesion scoring system (AFS 1988
             version) (19) showed in Table1 (AFS scoreâ‰¥5);

          2. Scheduled for hysteroscopic adhesiolysis;

